   "kind": 2,
   "value": "$Assumptions = {(q | q1 | q2 | p | t1 | t2 | hbar | m | x | \\[Sigma]x | \\[Sigma]p | \\[Sigma]q) \\[Element] Reals &&\r\nhbar > 0 && m > 0};\r\n\r\narg = exps[[2]] // Expand\r\n\r\nbd1 = Coefficient[arg, q1, 1] //FullSimplify;\r\ncd1 = Coefficient[arg, q1, 0] //FullSimplify;\r\n\r\nbI = -I(Im[bd1]) //FullSimplify \r\nbII = -(Re[bd1]) //FullSimplify \r\ncI = -cd1 //FullSimplify \r\n",
